</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B91BC26FF83631C7323034EFDFF46A2" blockId="20.[264,1323,1038,1785]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="B95A6034FF83631C7323034EFD49468B" bold="true" box="[312,684,1638,1664]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Derivation of specific epithet.</emphasis>
