<emphasis id="B95A6034FF83631C711D034FFC84468B" box="[774,865,1639,1664]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">simoma</emphasis>
(neut.), for turned up, referring to the shape of the ovipositor.
</paragraph>
